Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Updated cost calculator logic per requirements:

- Moved basement to Zone E (Rs 2700/sqft)
- Moved staircase to Zone B (50% rate, 125 sqft per floor)
- Updated water tank to Zone D (Rs 15/liter, 2000L per floor excluding stilt)
- Removed mumty from Zone B
- Updated stilt area calculation (Plot*Coverage - Lift - Staircase)
- Updated Zone C to Rs 600/sqft with terrace + ramp (6ft) + setback
- Ramp calculation: Breadth * 6ft
- Setback: Plot Area - Floor Area
- Updated water tank description to 'brickwork including waterproofing and tile'
